title: Population of Luxembourg 2019 , by age
summary: Overall Number of inhabitants has increased over the Year.
Number of inhabitants is slightly increasing from 45-49_years to 50-54_years.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 5-9_years and 50-54_years.
The highest Number of inhabitants, of value 46695.0 was reached at Year 50-54_years
Minimum Number of inhabitants about 33355.0 was reached at Year 5-9_years
